<section id="Section586876">
  <title><anchor id="Anchor586894" role="Index"
  xreflabel="tax types:master list of" /> <indexterm significance="normal"
      zone="Anchor587049">
      <primary>tax types</primary>

      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Tax Type</title>

  <para id="Para587050">To create a new Tax Type, select the NEW button. The
  following screen will appear:</para>

  <para id="Para587707"><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/GL_MI_taxTypeNew.png" id="Graphic587705" />
        </imageobject>

        <caption id="Caption587708">Create New Tax Type</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>

  <para id="Para587709">When creating a new Tax Type, you are presented with
  the following options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term id="Para587772">Name</term>

      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18adfd4">
        <para>Enter a name to describe the Tax Type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term id="Para587773">Description</term>

      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18ae01c">
        <para>Enter a description to further describe the Tax Type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

  <para id="Para587716">To the far right of the screen, the following buttons
  are available:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term id="Para587717">CANCEL</term>

      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18ae088">
        <para>Closes the screen without creating a Tax Type, returning you to
        the previous screen.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term id="Para587718">SAVE</term>

      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18ae0d0">
        <para>Creates the Tax Type and adds it to the master list of Tax
        Types.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>